});
```

These approaches are more readable and align better with modern JavaScript/TypeScript practices.
give me a one-liner for copying the commit message to the clipboard

Here's a one-liner to copy the last git commit message to the clipboard:

```bash
git log -1 --pretty=%B | pbcopy     # for macOS
# or
git log -1 --pretty=%B | clip       # for Windows
# or
git log -1 --pretty=%B | xclip -selection clipboard    # for Linux
```

Choose the appropriate one based on your operating system. `pbcopy` is for macOS, `clip` is for Windows, and `xclip` is for Linux.
